    General Stores in Prabhadevi, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. There's bound to be a general shop located at every other corner of any neighbourhood. As general stores, these establishments store items categorised as food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. These retail stores are a part of the sales network of most FMCG brands and leading manufacturing companies. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Catering to the convenience of their customers, these shops also extend free home delivery service. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. Mentioned above is a vast list of General Stores in Prabhadevi, Mumbai.
